These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, australian, turkish, canadian, british, brazilian, german
1. the australian is in the middle##1
2. the australian is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the british is on the right of the canadian##1
4. the pakistani is on the right of the turkish##1
5. the german is on the far left##1
6. the brazilian is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | german | canadian | british | australian | turkish | pakistani | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, designer, police-officer, dressmaker, project-manager, firefighter, mechanic
1. the mechanic is on the far right##1
2. the electrician is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the left of the project-manager##1
4. the project-manager is on the left of the police-officer##1
5. the dressmaker is on the right of the firefighter##1
6. the mechanic is on the right of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | electrician | project-manager | police-officer | firefighter | dressmaker | designer | mechanic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: gardening, singing, cooking, hiking, camping, chess, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | camping | gardening | chess | cooking | video-games | singing | hiking |

 #################################

 
