4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | cat | bird | goat | horse | hamster | dog | fish |

