1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | western | time-travel | romance | comedy | family | superhero | scientific |

